snippet.title: Millions of Americans Are Stuck and Can‚Äôt Sell Their Homes
snippet.description:
The American housing market is frozen, and millions of homeowners are finding themselves stuck with houses they simply can‚Äôt sell. What used to fly off the market in days is now sitting for months with little to no interest. Why is this happening? Rising interest rates, skyrocketing mortgage costs, unaffordable home prices, and a shrinking pool of qualified buyers are leaving the housing market at a standstill.

In this video, we‚Äôll break down why homes aren‚Äôt selling in 2025, the real reasons behind this housing crisis, and what it means for families across America. From record-high mortgage rates to buyers being priced out, the warning signs are everywhere. If you‚Äôve been watching the ‚ÄúFor Sale‚Äù signs sit in your neighborhood, you already know something is very wrong.

Now more than ever, Americans need to prepare, stay informed, and think smart about their financial future. The frozen housing market is just one piece of the bigger economic puzzle‚Äîand it‚Äôs a reminder of how fragile our system really is.

In this video, we‚Äôll break down why homes aren‚Äôt selling in 2025, the real reasons behind this housing crisis, and what it means for families across America. From record-high mortgage rates to buyers being priced out, the warning signs are everywhere. If you‚Äôve been watching the ‚ÄúFor Sale‚Äù signs sit in your neighborhood, you already know something is very wrong.

Now more than ever, Americans need to prepare, stay informed, and think smart about their financial future. The frozen housing market is just one piece of the bigger economic puzzle‚Äîand it‚Äôs a reminder of how fragile our system really is.

snippet.title: Raising a Large Family on My Own
snippet.description:
Welcome back friends (JAM FAM?! üëÄ???) Today I‚Äôm sharing a week in my life as a large family single mom of 9 raising a huge family on my own.

This week is packed with large family meal prep that I also film for other videos and we make our way through breakfasts, lunches, dinners, snacks, and desserts all week long (we eat it all‚Ä¶ Quickly‚Ä¶ Ha ha! ü§£). We get our daily miles in with walks, runs, and steps and of course there‚Äôs the big question everyone always wonders‚Ä¶ how many times can I go to Walmart or get Walmart deliveries in just one week or even in a day? It‚Äôs large family grocery shopping at its finest plus needed big family  household items and so much more.

There are so many playground trips, ice cream treats, and fun family outings like visiting the arboretum and in the middle of all that I‚Äôm also working full-time from home while keeping up with everything a large family needs 100% on my own. It‚Äôs busy, it‚Äôs messy, it‚Äôs fun, and pretty OK. I‚Äôm so glad you‚Äôre here to do this new universe life with me üíïüíïüíï

If you‚Äôve ever dreamed about becoming a full-time YouTuber to help provide for your family, I have a free masterclass where I share the five keys to YouTuber success and you can watch it right here: https://jamerrillstewart.easywebinar.live/event-registration-2 I‚Äôd love to teach you how to get started and make YouTube a success and help you get going on your dreams ü§ó
